    public class HL7Exception
extends AbstractHL7Exception

      • HL7Exception

        public HL7Exception(String message,
                    int errorCondition,
                    Throwable cause)
        Deprecated. use HL7Exception(String, ErrorCode, Throwable)
        Creates an HL7Exception.
        Parameters:
        errorCondition - a code describing the the error condition, from HL7 table 0357 (see section 2.16.8 of standard v 2.4) - ErrorCode defines these codes that can be used here (e.g. ErrorCode.UNSUPPORTED_MESSAGE_TYPE.getCode())
        cause - The exception that caused this exception to be thrown.
